      <title>阿斯利康受中国市场影响的股价暴跌或难以摆脱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/astrazeneca-azn-china-probe-puts-shares-on-track-for-worst-week-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周初，阿斯利康公司的市值约为 1710 亿英镑（2220 亿美元）。截至周四收盘，其市值已跌至略高于 1500 亿英镑，这家制药商已失去英国市值最大公司的地位，被壳牌公司取代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/astrazeneca-azn-china-probe-puts-shares-on-track-for-worst-week-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选当天，美国股市迎来 6 月份以来最大资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/us-stocks-draw-biggest-inflow-since-june-on-the-day-of-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师表示，唐纳德·特朗普在总统大选中取得决定性胜利的当天，周三有高达 200 亿美元的资金流入美国股票基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/us-stocks-draw-biggest-inflow-since-june-on-the-day-of-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:43:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克央行行长呼吁紧缩政策、削减预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/czech-central-bank-chief-urges-tight-policy-budget-austerity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克央行行长表示，全球利率需要高于冠状病毒大流行之前，并敦促各国政府平衡预算，以帮助控制通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/czech-central-bank-chief-urges-tight-policy-budget-austerity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛提拔德国合伙人人数达十年来最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/goldman-promotes-highest-number-of-german-partners-in-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团任命两名德国人为合伙人，这是十多年来最多的一次，因为这家华尔街银行希望在德国获得更多业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/goldman-promotes-highest-number-of-german-partners-in-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:39:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寿司的秘密录音帮助石油交易商提起伦敦偷猎诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/secret-recording-over-sushi-helps-oil-trader-bring-london-poaching-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国能源交易公司 Dare International Ltd. 起诉两名前交易员，指控他们“公然”违反雇佣条款，以“尽快赚取更多金钱”，然后加入该公司在迪拜的主要竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/secret-recording-over-sushi-helps-oil-trader-bring-london-poaching-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
